It's not just today, is it?

00:37:21.599 --> 00:37:23.280
It's been several days now.

00:37:23.400 --> 00:37:24.960
What's going on with you?

00:37:24.960 --> 00:37:26.039
If you're not feeling well,

00:37:26.039 --> 00:37:27.400
I'll take you to the hospital.

00:37:27.400 --> 00:37:28.519
No, no, don't.

00:37:28.519 --> 00:37:29.840
Stop, I'm fine.

00:37:30.360 --> 00:37:31.800
I'm begging you, okay?

00:37:31.800 --> 00:37:34.039
I'm begging you, don't disturb me.

00:37:36.039 --> 00:37:37.039
These past few days,

00:37:37.039 --> 00:37:38.920
you've been staying up late every night.

00:37:39.400 --> 00:37:41.599
You get up at dawn and start writing again.

00:37:41.960 --> 00:37:44.079
Are you trying to ruin your health?

00:37:44.840 --> 00:37:46.039
Stop writing.

00:37:46.239 --> 00:37:47.679
You need to eat properly.

00:37:48.360 --> 00:37:49.360
See, see?

00:37:49.360 --> 00:37:50.480
All my inspiration,

00:37:50.480 --> 00:37:53.079
you've just chattered it all away.

00:37:54.000 --> 00:37:55.559
Old lady, listen to me.

00:37:55.920 --> 00:37:58.360
The production company,

00:37:58.400 --> 00:38:01.199
they're meeting me in a couple of days.

00:38:01.360 --> 00:38:02.840
I'll just write for a little while, okay?

00:38:02.840 --> 00:38:03.719
Just a little while.

00:38:06.039 --> 00:38:08.559
Qiu'er isn't short of work.

00:38:11.920 --> 00:38:13.800
Where did you get that idea?

00:38:14.000 --> 00:38:16.480
I'm not writing for his sake.

00:38:16.480 --> 00:38:17.960
I'm doing it for myself.

00:38:18.480 --> 00:38:20.480
Don't think I don't know.

00:38:21.800 --> 00:38:23.480
Before Qiu'er quit his job,

00:38:23.480 --> 00:38:25.480
you weren't writing like this,

00:38:25.480 --> 00:38:27.440
day and night.

00:38:30.599 --> 00:38:33.760
Our Qiu'er is being so stubborn now,

00:38:34.159 --> 00:38:37.239
isn't it just to keep us old folks from worrying?

00:38:37.239 --> 00:38:37.960
Isn't that right?

