I interviewed with your company.

00:40:46.800 --> 00:40:47.599
May I trouble you to ask,

00:40:47.599 --> 00:40:49.159
do you have a result yet?

00:40:49.239 --> 00:40:50.400
Are you crazy?

00:40:50.679 --> 00:40:52.239
What time is it to be asking this?

00:40:52.400 --> 00:40:53.639
Don't I need to sleep?

00:40:53.920 --> 00:40:54.920
You don't even understand basic courtesy.

